## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Escopo de Negocio (Regra #5){{else}}Business Scope (Rule #5){{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
**PERMITIDO**: definicoes de tabelas (DDL), migrations (up/down), indices, constraints, validacao de contratos.

**PROIBIDO**: logica de negocio, ORM models com metodos de negocio, codigo de aplicacao, seeds com dados de negocio.
{{else}}
**ALLOWED**: table definitions (DDL), migrations (up/down), indexes, constraints, contract validation.

**FORBIDDEN**: business logic, ORM models with business methods, application code, seeds with business data.
{{/if}}

